{"type": "article", "id": 31695, "title": "裂缝中，它们透出来一点光｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-31T23:00:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 21703, "name": "Frederik Roijé"}, {"id": 32247, "name": "Fifth Column"}, {"id": 32248, "name": "Ceramic Japan"}, {"id": 32249, "name": "MINIMAL"}, {"id": 32250, "name": "Levko Davydiuk"}, {"id": 32251, "name": "Shareni De la Rosa"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 162, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160831235454VQquAIeaoXcm1MBj.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>SNOOZ by MINIMAL</h3><p>休息时你有没有因为房间里太过安静反而感到紧张？而在有背景音的情况下，无论是太响还是太轻都可能使人感到不安。为了创造出更舒适的休息环境，美国的 <a href=\"http://www.mnml.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MINIMAL</a> 公司就研发了一款能够形成白噪音的机器 SNOOZ。它内置了一个风扇，和其他依靠扬声器播放音乐的产品相比，发声方式要自然许多，而且还会时不时送出微微的凉风。这是它的<a href=\"https://getsnooz.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 79 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235645QgfOrIBALJapcZNd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235645O3XVGxvf7KoEuaLg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235645yrI1zMvO3qoNYxlE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235646wG3LJYAe6NX7f1Fz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235646WEhOM49uQPiHrmsk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235646sdqwxS32ZgTROPhY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sliced Sphere by Frederik Roijé</h3><p>荷兰设计品牌 <a href=\"http://www.roije.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Frederik Roijé</a> 将在巴黎时尚家居设计展秋展上展出的最新作品是一系列名为 Sliced Sphere 的球形吊灯，借助造型与光源产生互动，营造出令人称奇的视觉效果。亮灯后，光线会从灯罩表面倾斜的裂缝中透出，仿佛灯罩的下半部分就是通过这条光带与上半部分“若即若离”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608312356319qdvZVtD736Wk4XM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332518\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235630DOwh0agGUFvl1mBy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235630pQokOEdBC38xL0AZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235630iOKmq8N74Zy0Jl9z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235630uYNzlR3nEVLkrUjJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235631FyBHirZfYRWgd0AX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332518\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Reo by Fifth Column</h3><p>第一眼看到这款名为 Reo 的座椅时，你或许会因为混凝土底座认定它无法移动，事实上它仅有 8 公斤重。虽然印度设计咨询公司 <a href=\"http://fifthcolumn.in/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fifth Column</a> 的确是以建筑地基为灵感进行的设计，但设计师们更希望能够借此挑战混凝土和钢筋粗犷的特性。和四四方方的混凝土结构柱不同，Reo 的底座像是一个灰色的木塞；黄色座椅则采用了符合人体工程学的设计，由一根根被折成特定角度的钢筋组合而成，不仅简洁也富有趣味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608312357053WKIQt4iUlOLAayE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235705BSDQxV8ejwAzn3Gb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235705TadCWZSwkHu501yi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235705D8KlI5bB2O6peQxj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235705oELHYlUPFWRSceB5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Neo+ by Ceramic Japan</h3><p>在日本的陶器之城爱知县濑户市，陶器制造商 <a href=\"http://www.ceramic-japan.co.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ceramic Japan</a> 与著名陶艺大师<a href=\"http://www.makoto-komatsu.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">小松誠</a>联手打造了这套名为 Neo+ 的陶瓷花器。弯弯曲曲的圆柱形花器既像是植物的茎，又仿佛是随着海浪摇动的珊瑚。这些花器分为两种款式，台式的底部和壁式的侧面都装有磁铁，可以吸附在配套的铁板或是墙面上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235731uGEFYcU1XmVNJzMk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235730NgA1RCbO6SIxv8hq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.348315\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235731nWvd4JfQ2uYhkTR0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235731nUIW1NLiRsQGBv90.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016083123573046fsEjBpVSrDLqIW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.293103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235731SrcAR2q0zfxhJZWT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.348315\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ZEX bookshelves by Levko Davydiuk</h3><p>如果你看过电影《盗梦空间》，乌克兰设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/leoduk\" rel=\"nofollow\">Levko Davydiuk</a> 打造的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/42159919/ZEX-bookshelves\" rel=\"nofollow\">ZEX</a> 系列或许会让你回忆起片中对于物品以及空间那天马行空的操纵：一个同样具有收纳功能的金属柜倾斜着穿插进木制的立式和壁式书架之中，重新划分了整件家具的布局。Davydiuk 还将柜子与底座设计在一起，使立式书架拥有水平和垂直放置两种款式。当家里摆上这么一个书架时，你或许会对该怎么摆书和其他装饰品有更多的思考。美中不足的是 ZEX 仍是一款概念设计，尚未投入实际生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160901000257fqhVMuorkYUia352.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160901000258sX8MEbItfDZHkeyR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160901000300vcMFk96KX13yJPRO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160901000300ca5sO1jNAtPQJHLT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160901000300o5iGFjqP9Qk1Vazc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160901000323EFiZN0o8ezBCmIwk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.510000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>FLAMINGO by Shareni De la Rosa</h3><p>还记得我们之前介绍的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/30173.html\">火烈鸟茶具</a>吗？来自墨西哥的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/sharenirx\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shareni De la Rosa</a> 同样借鉴了这种修长而美丽的动物造型，打造了一款以它为名的模块式边桌 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/30967007/FLAMINGO\" rel=\"nofollow\">FLAMINGO</a>。它的桌面实际上是三块堆叠在一起的托盘，侧面看上去就像是一只低着头的火烈鸟。不需要使用边桌时，你还可以把托盘拆卸下来单独使用，非常灵活。目前 FLAMINGO 还是一款概念设计，尚未投入实际生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235836crJuwO8xN4FBR62o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235837KgDPJmq7Y3Z9wCdc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.924286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235837p2M8nAlLvVE9Rbf6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.924286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608312358364Czg8sb3KXyTYJtH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.927273\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016083123583674hY3Gv9QdAu6SDJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.924286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160831235838qTYzaub8OjQRtSn3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.924286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}